---
title: Double Soy-Ginger Glazed White Fish with Garlicky Stir-Fried Greens
description: A little sweet, a little savoury and a whole lot of delicious! This delicate fish dish is beautifully tender and packed with umami-rich flavour, paired with garlicky stir-fried greens for the perfect balance. Light, tasty, and totally satisfying - you’re in for a real treat tonight!

*We’ve replaced the broccoli florets in this recipe with green beans
due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
